These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: woodworking, fishing, magic-tricks, filmmaking, sudoku
There are 5 different nationalities: dutch, indian, egyptian, american, spanish
5 different pets are kept: lizard, chinchilla, fish, ferret, pony
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: snowboarding, ice-hockey, biathlon, tennis, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the dutch##1
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the egyptian##1
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is the american##1
 6. the indian is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 8. the indian is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the indian##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
12. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | fishing  | woodworking    | filmmaking | magic-tricks    | sudoku  |
| Nationality   | indian  | dutch | egyptian | american | spanish  |
| Pet           | lizard     | pony     | ferret  | chinchilla   | fish    |
| Sport         | biathlon | tennis    | ice-hockey | snowboarding  | volleyball |

