.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There 5 different types of food: lemon, apple, mango, pear, apricot
The people have 5 different jobs:  manager, security-guard, pilot, project-manager, software-developer
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, sports, drama, zombie
There are 5 different nationalities: italian, egyptian, dutch, polish, australian
 1. the project-manager is on the right of the italian##1
 2. the dutch is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the egyptian is on the right of the polish##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 6. the pilot is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 7. the software-developer is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 8. the person eating mango is the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the polish is the person eating mango##1
10. the person eating apple is in the middle##1
11. the person eating pear is on the left of the dutch##1
12. the person eating mango is the security-guard##1
13. the person eating apricot is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Food          | mango        | apricot | apple     | pear      | lemon  |
| Job           | security-guard   | pilot | software-developer    | project-manager | manager |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | drama     | zombie | musical    | mystery  |
| Nationality   | polish     | egyptian | italian    | australian      | dutch    |

