.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, mirinda, iced-tea, juice
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, camping, gardening, sudoku, woodworking
There are 5 different nationalities: mexican, thai, nigerian, italian, french
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, trike, airplane, boat, car
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the french##1
 2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the mexican is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is in the middle##1
 5. the nigerian is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the nigerian is on the right of the italian##1
 9. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the thai##1
11. the nigerian is the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
13. the person drinking iced-tea is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea          | mirinda  | soy-milk       | almond-milk     | juice      |
| Hobby         | camping | woodworking | sudoku  | gardening   | baking    |
| Nationality   | thai        | french | mexican | italian    | nigerian   |
| Transport     | bus   | airplane | car      | trike | boat |

