.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
There 5 different types of food: peas, pineapple, garlic, apple, nectarine
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, fantasy, comedy, crime, epic
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, rock, soul, blues, folk
The people use 5 different means of transport: quad-bike, motorbike, subway, train, bus
 1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 3. the fan of rock is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the fan of hip-hop is the person watching thriller movies##1
 5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 8. the person driving the bus is in the middle##1
 9. the fan of blues is on the left of the person eating peas##1
10. the person eating nectarine is the fan of soul##1
11. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food          | apple        | peas       | garlic | pineapple   | nectarine  |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | comedy | fantasy | thriller   | crime |
| Music-Genre   | blues         | folk     | rock | hip-hop | soul     |
| Transport     | quad-bike        | motorbike        | bus    | train    | subway      |

