 4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the person watching documentary movies is the owner of the rat##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person drinking water##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
12. the person watching sports movies is the fan of hip-hop##1
13. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage      | sprite      | lemonade       | coffee         | water  | mirinda |
| Movie-Genre   | sports  | superhero | documentary | thriller  | fantasy  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | salsa    | soul        | d&b | metal     |
| Pet           | hamster | lizard      | rat       | chinchilla   | fish   |

